Gateway checks for value in AssignTo_Group_Id or AssignTo_User_Id If either one of them have value, it means UI has selected for a user or the group for further assignments. Based on that, flow goes to Group Task or an individual task.

Who Assigned is added because of following - Scenario - When Principal Appraiser (PA) performs a direct assignment to an Appraiser and PA selects the option of "Return-To to 'Assigning Manager'" When Appraiser Submits the task,task gets assigned to PA, due to following reason. The assigning manager is PA and not the supervisor, because task has arrived to Appraiser from PA and not a supervisor.
As we need to follow the convention that, on submit by appraiser, task should never reach to PA, then we have to route the task to Appraiser's direct manager.
